languages.text: «Idira, shereen, ignoren a la kassha. Escúchenme a mí: hemos preparado algo especial en las cubiertas centrales en su honor...».
languages.original_text: "Idira, shereen, don't listen to that kassha. Listen to me instead — wait until you see what we have planned on the middle decks in your honour..."

languages.text: 「シャリーン、あのカッシャの言葉を聞いてはいけないわ。代わりにあたしの言葉を聞いて。イディラちゃんの名誉のためにも、あたしたちが中層デッキで計画していることを見るまで待っていてちょうだい…」
languages.original_text: "Idira, shereen, don't listen to that kassha. Listen to me instead — wait until you see what we have planned on the middle decks in your honour..."

languages.text: “伊迪拉，亲爱的，别听那个小贱人的话。还是听我的话吧，好好等着，看我们在中层甲板为你准备了什么好东西……”
languages.original_text: "Idira, shereen, don't listen to that kassha. Listen to me instead — wait until you see what we have planned on the middle decks in your honour..."

languages.text: "Idira, Shereen, hört nicht auf diese kassha. Hört lieber auf mich ... wartet, bis Ihr seht, was wir auf den Mitteldecks geplant haben, um Euch zu ehren ..."
languages.original_text: "Idira, shereen, don't listen to that kassha. Listen to me instead — wait until you see what we have planned on the middle decks in your honour..."

languages.text: « Idira, shereen, n'écoutez pas cette kassha. Attendez plutôt de voir ce qu'on a prévu en votre honneur sur les ponts intermédiaires… »
languages.original_text: "Idira, shereen, don't listen to that kassha. Listen to me instead — wait until you see what we have planned on the middle decks in your honour..."
